                            <comment id="16206887" author="catholicon" created="Tue, 17 Oct 2017 01:33:21 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Attaching &lt;span class=&quot;nobr&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/attachment/12892503/12892503_OAK-6838.patch&quot; title=&quot;OAK-6838.patch attached to OAK-6838&quot;&gt;OAK-6838.patch&lt;sup&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rendericon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/link_attachment_7.gif&quot; height=&quot;7&quot; width=&quot;7&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; with tests and potential fix (this doesn&apos;t break any tests in oak-core or oak-jcr... haven&apos;t tested all modules)&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16220168" author="tmueller" created="Thu, 26 Oct 2017 08:40:48 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Sounds reasonable, but possibly it&apos;s a compatibility problem (with Jackrabbit 2.x, but also with older versions of Oak). So if you fix this, I suggest to add a feature flag (system property) so people can re-enable it if needed, until they can fix their application.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16247003" author="catholicon" created="Fri, 10 Nov 2017 04:44:55 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;del&gt;Fixed in trunk at &lt;a href=&quot;https://svn.apache.org/r1814817&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;r1814817&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/del&gt; Reverted the fix at &lt;a href=&quot;https://svn.apache.org/r1814821&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;r1814821&lt;/a&gt; as it broke &lt;tt&gt;org.apache.jackrabbit.oak.jcr.query.QueryTest.relativeNotExistsProperty&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;SegmentTar&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/tt&gt; [0]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;[0]: &lt;a href=&quot;https://builds.apache.org/job/Jackrabbit%20Oak/961/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://builds.apache.org/job/Jackrabbit%20Oak/961/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16247165" author="catholicon" created="Fri, 10 Nov 2017 08:08:48 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Finally done in trunk at &lt;a href=&quot;https://svn.apache.org/r1814822&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;r1814822&lt;/a&gt;. To maintain compatibility with Jr2 or older oak versions(&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OAK-1085&quot; title=&quot;Compatibility for queries with not(child/@prop) conditions&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;OAK-1085&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;OAK-1085&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;), &lt;tt&gt;-Doak.useOldInexistenceCheck=true&lt;/tt&gt; can be passed on JVM command line.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16283608" author="edivad" created="Fri, 8 Dec 2017 14:23:53 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Bulk close 1.7.12&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
